Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈 龍捲風裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在動！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎 艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎 要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛兵 衛兵在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著王宮去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:17.87,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1500)\pos(258,568)\blur2}各自的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有來王宮避難的人就放進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 你有什麼辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫險了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來毀滅和死亡的不詳象徵 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說萊菈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻龍也是污穢造成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在還不敢相信自己的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍竟然真的出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你拯救了瑞迪雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師保護了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 導師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻龍是靠導師大人的力量抵擋住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太謙虛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師大人 我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為感謝 我想招待您進餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以賞光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾托洛卿 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 我不知道你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想盡力為導師大人消除疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師大人接受我的邀請了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎也能一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 請停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞迪雷克雖然還沒完有完全被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但時間也所剩無幾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想想辦法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎殿下就那樣呆著 我來送您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王陛下傳話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快前往王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等著您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎不想讓艾莉莎同席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼導師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您導師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師大人和艾莉莎公主是什麼樣的關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然認識還沒多久 但我覺得是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能和我成為朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我做朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 不要輕易喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還和您胃口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是海蘭德的特產
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為最近連續災害收成不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼話要對我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導師大人今後有什麼打算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說務必想藉助導師大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去追龍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追龍…想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但龍是不詳的象徵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡也許就會有改善世界的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候不早了 今天就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 我要去馬林頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是國王陛下的親令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個叫巴爾托洛的人搞的鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是即使是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能對受疫病折磨的人們棄之不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎 就那樣放走了導師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要離開瑞迪雷克的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在也沒有必要在這裡流血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼戰爭的準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈 可以談談嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎 米克里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到今天的史雷我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷成為了導師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在直視著他的命運前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得他成了遙不可及的存在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼米克里歐今後打算怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不知道 雖然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得至今的關係將無法持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷成了導師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我該做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然打算暫時和史雷一起旅行才離開了故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回伊子集去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 雖然也有過這個念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷如果今後要作為導師周遊世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法丟下他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里歐真的很喜歡史雷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是孽緣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里歐能為史雷做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈 馬上去追米克里歐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到憑魔的話他一個人該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事他應該明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說米克里歐有他的理由才會一個人離開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去追他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為真正的導師我也有我該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了瑞迪雷克之後一直向北走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會到達一片很大的湖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有一座被稱為「戈爾哈多」的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座遺跡裡沉睡著可以鎮魔的傳說中的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的聖劍是相同的東西 是聖遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里歐能得到那個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能靠自己幫助史雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出發了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情的發展可不等人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉這麼晚才還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米克里歐從遺跡撿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中途就行 可以來做我們的守衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家第一次親眼見到了龍的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說揭開了它的面紗成為了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傳說中有線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈峰雷弗爾克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屢次在龍的傳說中登場的人跡罕至的險峰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是長尾怪 只生活在這座森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 是很溫順的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 是什麼憑魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蛇還是蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈大人真的不用吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只喝點飲料也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近結的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銼碎了以後用熱水煮成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酸 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長尾怪竟然會襲擊人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再經過兩座村子 渡過一條大河就是馬林頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個什麼樣的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人口僅次於瑞迪雷克 也是陪都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化水準很高 識字率在國內最高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經也是父親引以為豪的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疫病的影響有那麼嚴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是醫師團 也不知道會有多大效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以談談史雷的話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前聽你說過沒有離開過伊子集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是嬰兒的時候發生了一場大火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺似乎從那裡救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就一直在伊子集裡生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然沒能和他交談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一定是一位了不起的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是被爺爺的加護保護著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到下界才終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你一開始就看得見天族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是看得見的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說是因為一起生活才感知到天族的存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多了解一些天族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天遺見聞錄裡也寫到過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太古時代 人類感知天族和他們共同生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天族們在不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作土守護大地 化作風支撐天空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作水潤澤河流 化作火維繫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持著它們的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土 風 水 火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 天族也不是萬能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有擅長和不擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈是火屬性的天族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里歐擅長操縱水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們卻無法再感知到天族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才產生了這個災難的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類忘記了對天族的崇敬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心充滿了懷疑 邪念以及爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也就是說災難是人心所孕育的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個世界充滿了污穢是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問災難也正在擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想創造天族和人類能夠共存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷在伊子集是這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議我記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為史雷小時候起就和天族一起生活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單身一人也不會寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很符合導師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我從沒感到過寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有米克里歐在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈說得沒錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近應該會有遺蹟的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能輸給他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是雷弗爾克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是我贏了呢 史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我贏了 米克里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的月亮真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米克里歐也在哪裡看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈 為什麼愁眉苦臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮了一下有關淨化的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨化麼 很複雜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛成為導師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話也不知道能把這個世界淨化成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.87,0:23:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想在旅行中鍛煉作為導師的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能淨化這個世上的污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷竟然也在考慮淨化的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是導師 這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 萊菈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有靈感了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來淨化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史雷 和米克里歐吵架也太衝動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很「淨化」吧 鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你考慮的是冷笑話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週「靈峰雷弗爾克」 敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊菈 那女孩是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:06.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}向著遙遠前方的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你順風而行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:16.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}追尋的答案不易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:20.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}從開始就已明白才跨出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:30.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}夢想的足跡 無數次繞遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:34.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}將描繪好的世界地圖展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}迴響吧！風之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:43.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}閉上眼睛 心中的聲音鼓舞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:49.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}目的地還在更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:52.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}傳遞吧！風之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:57.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}側耳傾聽 心中的聲音滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:02.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}釋放出耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你化為藍色的旋律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:59.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}此刻閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:07.55,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在這不歸的旅途上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:13.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在片刻的安寧中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:19.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我們懷著願望入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:27.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}夢中的世界被光明照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:34.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}滿溢的熱情 寄宿著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:42.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}為了明天暫作休憩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:48.43,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我們現在在這裡歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:54.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}它將在這旅途的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:22:01.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}一定會抓住命運的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:07.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在此時此處描繪著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:12.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:19.10,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}共同前行